about it.

26:39.331 --> 26:40.732 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

26:40.766 --> 26:42.468 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: But the friend who
showed O'Bannon
the game was puzzled.

26:42.501 --> 26:47.706 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ED O'BANNON: What's funny about
it is, he
says, we paid X-amount of
dollars for it,

26:47.739 --> 26:49.842 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
for the video game, and you
