penny.

26:49.875 --> 26:54.947 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
PAUL SOLMAN: It was this
encounter that sparked
a famous firestorm, Ed
O'Bannon's eventual

26:54.980 --> 27:04.523 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
2009 lawsuits against the NCAA
and video game
maker EA Sports for blatant and
unlawful use

27:04.556 --> 27:11.263 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
