27:43.529 --> 27:47.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: We'd come to find
out what's
happened to Ed O'Bannon and his
suit, landing

27:47.866 --> 27:54.540 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
