book, "Indentured."

28:28.807 --> 28:34.212 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JOE NOCERA, Author,
"Indentured": They are
fundamentally exploited by a
system that makes

28:34.246 --> 28:42.220 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
