29:12.818 --> 29:13.452 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
PAUL SOLMAN: You?

29:13.485 --> 29:15.187 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ED O'BANNON: Oh, absolutely.

29:15.220 --> 29:17.456 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN: It's simple, gentlemen. The
little things
is what's going to win us the
game.

29:17.489 --> 29:23.829 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: Back at Liberty
High, the coaches
