Emmert.

32:06.191 --> 32:07.959 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MARK EMMERT: He's allowed his
opinions.

32:07.993 --> 32:13.365 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: Turns out it's not
